Dialogue: 3,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“这房子装修的可真漂亮，夫人! ”
Dialogue: 2,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'What a lovely house you've made, my lady!'
Dialogue: 3,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这里建一个露台花园
Dialogue: 2,0:00:31.96,0:00:33.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll build a terrace garden here.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你知道，那些小型植物和树木?-盆景
Dialogue: 2,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You know, with those miniature plants and trees? - Bonsai.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}‘盆景，我听说会带来幸运’
Dialogue: 2,0:00:37.24,0:00:39.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Bonsai. We'll plant those too. I've heard they are very lucky.'
Dialogue: 3,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:47.24,0:00:48.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What is it?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你没事吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.80,0:00:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我该说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.16,0:00:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I say?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你告诉我，你工作还好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You tell me. Is everything okay at work?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:55.44,0:00:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:00:55.44,0:00:56.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 3,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的业务超出了我的理解范围
Dialogue: 2,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Your business is beyond my understanding.
Dialogue: 3,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我知道所有的报纸都在报道你
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I do understand that all the newspapers are writing about you.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那就让他们报道吧
Dialogue: 2,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So let them.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毫无价值的新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:01:03.40,0:01:04.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's worthless news.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多亏了你丈夫，许多家庭才得以经营
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.08,0:01:08.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Many homes run thanks to your husband, my lady.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新闻记者就是其中之一
Dialogue: 2,0:01:09.12,0:01:10.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}News reporters are amongst them.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-就让他们也赚点钱吧-我害怕
Dialogue: 2,0:01:10.88,0:01:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- So, let them earn too. - I'm scared.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这次感觉不一样了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:14.72,0:01:16.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It feels different this time.
Dialogue: 3,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有什么不同？
Dialogue: 2,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's different?
Dialogue: 3,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你想太多了-嘿！
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- You think too much. - Hey!
Dialogue: 3,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不会占用太多的时间
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I won't take up too much of your time.'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:02:28.48,0:02:29.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I know...'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 你们中的大多数人在这里... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.76,0:02:32.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that most of you are here...'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只为了听一个人的话
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.24,0:02:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to listen to just one man.'
Dialogue: 3,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}据我所知，他是个科学家
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}According to me, he's a scientist.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场的爱因斯坦
Dialogue: 2,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Einstein of the share market.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德 · 梅塔
Dialogue: 2,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad Mehta. Please, come.
Dialogue: 3,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢你
Dialogue: 2,0:02:59.96,0:03:01.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老实说，我连爱因斯坦这个词都拼不出来
Dialogue: 2,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}To be honest, I can't even spell 'Einstein'.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不过没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But that's okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:11.88,0:03:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很新鲜
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.88,0:03:12.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's new.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些天，人们也叫我股市的小偷
Dialogue: 2,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}These days, people are also calling me the thief of the stock market.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}报纸称我为“大牛” ..
Dialogue: 2,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The newspapers refer to me as "Big Bull"...
Dialogue: 3,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“大牛带着印度国家银行的50亿卢比跑了”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:23.08,0:03:25.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Big Bull has run away with 500 crores from SBI."
Dialogue: 3,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这意味着我吞掉了 SBI 的50亿
Dialogue: 2,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They mean I have swallowed up SBI's 500 crore.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我不得不吞下钱，为什么只有50亿？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If at all I had to swallow money, why just 500 crores?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.92,0:03:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}货币市场设立了一个每日自助餐... 两万亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The money market sets up a daily buffet... of two lakh crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以想象一下，哈尔沙德 · 梅塔的日常交易会是什么样子！
Dialogue: 2,0:03:42.64,0:03:46.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So imagine. What Harshad Mehta's daily transactions would be!
Dialogue: 3,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他们不会以我的名字命名
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But they aren't taking my name.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只是写“大牛”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.52,0:03:53.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They just write "Big Bull".
Dialogue: 3,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大家都知道，我是大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:03:54.88,0:03:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, everyone knows, I am the Big Bull.
Dialogue: 3,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“嗯? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'Hmm?'
Dialogue: 3,0:04:00.00,0:04:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是，我大公牛与安全交易有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.00,0:04:05.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But what does my being the Big Bull have to do with the reconciliation of security transactions?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}间接地说，他们想表达的是..
Dialogue: 2,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Indirectly what they're trying to say is...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要为市场的牛市负责
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.12,0:04:12.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that I am responsible for the bull run in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay. That's fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这也意味着... 如果不是因为我..
Dialogue: 2,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But that also means... if it wasn't for me...
Dialogue: 3,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场会像牛车一样缓慢前进吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the market would be lumbering along at the pace of a bullock cart?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}实际上报纸没有证据
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.88,0:04:28.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The truth is that the newspapers have no proof.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是为什么他们没有公开我的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's why they aren't taking my name openly.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为他们说的都是假话
Dialogue: 2,0:04:32.52,0:04:34.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because there's no truth in what they're saying.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我从 SBI 拿了50亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I took 500 crores from SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，是真的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:39.64,0:04:40.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, it's true. I did.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我也把它退了回去
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.56,0:04:42.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I also returned it.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就算登报了又怎样？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How about printing that? Hmm?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他们不会
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.60,0:04:47.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But they won't.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为，如果它不是负面的，它就不是新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because, if it's not negative, it's not news.
Dialogue: 3,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}报纸需要卖出去，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:53.24,0:04:54.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The newspaper needs to sell, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们也需要赚钱糊口，不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They too have homes to run, don't they?
Dialogue: 3,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他们毫无根据的新闻吓不倒我
Dialogue: 2,0:04:59.56,0:05:02.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But their baseless and biased news doesn't scare me.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我为什么要害怕？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why should I be scared?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为我打破了外资银行在货币市场的垄断地位？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Because I've broken the monopoly of foreign banks in the money market?
Dialogue: 3,0:05:13.88,0:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在孟买..
Dialogue: 2,0:05:13.88,0:05:14.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In Mumbai...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每天早上当股票市场的钟声敲响的时候
Dialogue: 2,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...every morning when the gong is struck at the stock market...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的名字也随之被吟诵
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...my name is chanted along with it.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里是孟买
Dialogue: 2,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is Bombay.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这里，一切都会改变..
Dialogue: 2,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here, everything will change...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但海洋永远在那里
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...but the ocean will always be there.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，我就是达拉街（印度华尔街）的海洋
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.08,0:05:35.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, I am the ocean of Dalal Street.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你有胆量，你就能尝到盐的味道
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you have the guts, you can taste the salt.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们说交易所将在二十八号重新开放
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They say the market will reopen on the 28th.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}罢工即将结束
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.64,0:05:53.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The strike will be over.
Dialogue: 3,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果印度证交所主席已经接受了他们的要求... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.88,0:05:58.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If the SEBI chairman had already accepted their demands...
Dialogue: 3,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那为什么要把罢工拖延这么久？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then what was the point of stretching the strike on for so long?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:02.08,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-阿什温，我觉得...-你的想法完全正确
Dialogue: 2,0:06:02.08,0:06:04.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Ashwin Bhai, I think... - Your thoughts are absolutely right, Bhushan.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这篇文章的发表，这次罢工的延续..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:05.20,0:06:07.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The publishing of this article, the extension of the strike...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一切都计划得太周密，时机也太巧妙了
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.68,0:06:09.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's all been too well-planned and timed.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因此，只要一开市，股价就会持续下跌
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.64,0:06:12.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So that, as soon as the market opens the sentiment is low and it crashes...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你和我都明白，但我们都是笨蛋，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.24,0:06:14.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You and I get it, but we are duffers, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是这个家伙..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:14.80,0:06:15.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But this fellow...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个天才,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a genius,
Dialogue: 3,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股市的“爱因斯坦”
Dialogue: 2,0:06:17.76,0:06:18.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Einstein" of the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他已经飘了，看看他
Dialogue: 2,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}His brain has stopped working. Look at him.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你应该听听他的演讲
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You should've heard his speech.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个苏切塔 · 达拉尔没有任何名字
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That Sucheta Dalal didn't take any names.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他... 他公开承认..
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he... he confessed publicly...
Dialogue: 3,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我就是市场的大公牛”
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"I am the Big Bull of the market."
Dialogue: 3,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 大家为他鼓掌-罪犯才会招供
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- A round of applause for him. - Confessions are made by criminals.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只陈述事实
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I only stated facts.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这也只是为了没有人能够反对我们
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that too, only so that nobody can take a stand against us.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的有什么不对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And what is wrong with what I said?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们要隐瞒什么? 我要隐瞒什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do we have to hide? What should I hide?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在，即使是 SBI 也确认他们已经收到了资金
Dialogue: 2,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, even SBI has confirmed that they've received their money.
Dialogue: 3,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么了? 有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So? What's the issue?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你为什么不也告诉大家，偿还 SBI 的钱从哪里来呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.44,0:06:55.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then, why don't you also tell everyone where the money to repay SBI came from?
Dialogue: 3,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 对吧?-阿什温
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Right? - Ashwin Bhai...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(拉杰迪普)“因此，我是说这不是头版新闻”
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.88,0:07:04.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rajdeep] 'Therefore, I was saying it's not a front-page story.'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}接下来的故事会是怎样的？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What will the follow-up story be?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德承认他从 SBI 那里拿了钱
Dialogue: 2,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is admitting that he took money from SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使在我看来，这似乎是他与银行打交道的日常事务
Dialogue: 2,0:07:09.08,0:07:11.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Even to me, it seems like a daily deal that he does regularly with banks.'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就连印度国家银行的官员也在说同样的话
Dialogue: 2,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Even SBI officials are saying the same thing.'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快，人们就会质疑我们..
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Soon, people are going to question us...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}质疑我们的动机！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...about our motive!
Dialogue: 3,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德让我们看起来像个八卦杂志
Dialogue: 2,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is making us look like a f*****g gossip magazine.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但是哈尔沙德需要被绳之以法...-听我说，苏切塔
Dialogue: 2,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But Harshad needs to be brought to justice... - Listen to me, Sucheta.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德是一个英雄，一个普通人眼中的英雄
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.40,0:07:25.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad is a hero. A hero for the common man.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他在为他的客户、投资人赚钱
Dialogue: 2,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}His clients, his investors. He's making profits for them.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}人们倾向于相信他所说的一切
Dialogue: 2,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}People are inclined to believe whatever he says...
Dialogue: 3,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管我们怎么写他
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.48,0:07:33.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in spite of what we write against him.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[拉杰迪普]“相反，你为什么不写... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rajdeep] 'Instead, why don't you write about...'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 永无休止的经纪人罢工? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...the never-ending brokers' strike at the BSE?'
Dialogue: 3,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你到底在说什么，拉杰迪普?-是啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.84,0:07:39.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What are you even saying, Rajdeep? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，这是个好故事，你知道的
Dialogue: 2,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No. This is a good story and you know it.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:44.12,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想你们一定读过《印度时报》上的那篇文章吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.12,0:07:48.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm sure you've read the article that appeared in Times of India?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:49.20,0:07:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，市场上的大公牛和证券问题
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.20,0:07:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, sir. The Big Bull and the securities reconciliation issue.
Dialogue: 3,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:07:52.28,0:07:53.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Big Bull! -[smirks]
Dialogue: 3,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真不戳! 有什么新鲜事吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Great! So, what's new?
Dialogue: 3,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们知道这会发生，但是我们什么也没做
Dialogue: 2,0:07:58.04,0:08:01.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We knew this could happen. And yet, we did nothing.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们已经怀疑了一年了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We were suspecting this for a year, now.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，我们去年已经发布了指导方针，但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:06.80,0:08:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, we had issued guidelines last year, sir but...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么指导方针？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What... What guidelines are we talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This one?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}”从 PDO 返回 SGL 表格的任何实例... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:12.40,0:08:14.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Any instance of return of SGL form from the PDO..."
Dialogue: 3,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 因为帐户缺少足够的余额... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...for want of sufficient balance in the account..."
Dialogue: 3,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 应立即通知储备银行... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...should be immediately brought to the Reserve Bank's notice..."
Dialogue: 3,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 所有交易的细节”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...with the details of the transactions."
Dialogue: 3,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我敢肯定，一半的银行根本没看过
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm sure, half the people didn't even get it.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}剩下一半
Dialogue: 2,0:08:25.56,0:08:26.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the rest...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们直接用来擦屁股
Dialogue: 2,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They just wiped and flushed it.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:28.68,0:08:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[穆克吉]“先生... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:08:28.68,0:08:29.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Mukherjee] 'Sir...'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们该怎么办，先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How do we proceed, sir?
Dialogue: 3,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}利用你在每家银行的信息来源
Dialogue: 2,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Use your sources with every bank.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有... ... 进行一次粗略的审计
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.12,0:08:40.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] 'And... Conduct a rough audit.'
Dialogue: 3,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看看这些垃圾已经传播了多远..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Find out how far this garbage has spread...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:43.44,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后我们就会知道这个骗局的严重程度
Dialogue: 2,0:08:43.44,0:08:47.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and then we will know the extent of this scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:52.16,0:08:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:52.16,0:08:52.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.44,0:08:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look...
Dialogue: 3,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉杰迪普是对的
Dialogue: 2,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...Rajdeep is right.
Dialogue: 3,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请别介意，但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.84,0:09:01.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得我们太着急了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.72,0:09:03.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...I think we rushed the story.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们? 为什么是”我们” ? 你可以直接怪我
Dialogue: 2,0:09:03.40,0:09:05.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We? Why "we"? You can blame me directly.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:05.72,0:09:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是在怪你，苏切塔，我不是在怪你
Dialogue: 2,0:09:05.72,0:09:08.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not blaming you, Sucheta. I'm not blaming.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是说也许..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:08.88,0:09:10.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I was just saying, that maybe...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们多调查一些..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:10.96,0:09:12.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...if we had investigated more...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多研究一点，然后我们可以..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:12.76,0:09:14.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...researched a bit more then we could've...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是... 如果我们能找到..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, what I mean is that... if we could have found someone...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}愿意公开声明的人，那我们就有..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who was willing to go on record then we'd have...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在一家日报社工作
Dialogue: 2,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Debashis, I work for a daily newspaper.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不像你一样为杂志社工作
Dialogue: 2,0:09:22.44,0:09:24.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't work for a magazine, like you...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以坐下来好好思考，因为我有几个星期的时间交稿
Dialogue: 2,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that I can sit back and think because I have a few weeks.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我每天都有最后期限
Dialogue: 2,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have a deadline, daily.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我再继续等，就不会有这样的故事了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I'd have waited, I wouldn't have had a story.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道哈尔沙德 · 梅塔是个该死的骗子
Dialogue: 2,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know Harshad Mehta is a bloody scamster.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道吗? 如果他们想要一个该死的后续..
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You know what? If they want a goddamn follow up...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我会找到的-苏切塔，听着
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...I am gonna find one. - Sucheta, listen.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，你……
Dialogue: 2,0:09:35.60,0:09:38.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta... Look, you...
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你生我的气，可以让我离开
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] 'If you are mad at me, I'll leave.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你为什么要离开自己的房子？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.40,0:09:41.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why are you leaving your own house?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别这样，苏切塔
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Come on, Sucheta.
Dialogue: 3,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[苏切塔]“交易所终于重新开放了”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'Finally the market opened.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我仍然没有任何针对哈萨德的书面证据”
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I still had no paper evidence against Harshad.'
Dialogue: 3,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是他已经提前承认了这篇文章是关于他的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'But he had gone ahead and admitted that the article was about him.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“他试图淡化自己与 SBI 之间的问题... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:10:01.88,0:10:04.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'He was trying to downplay his problems with SBI...'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}希望市场不会有反应
Dialogue: 2,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...in the hope that the markets would not react...'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“但是人们似乎对哈尔沙德失去了信任”
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...but it seemed that the people had lost trust in Harshad.'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“高摩资本投资的股票直线下跌... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:10:12.92,0:10:16.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'It was a free fall for the shares in which Growmore was investing...'
Dialogue: 3,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果不能保持在4000点，它将进一步下跌
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If it doesn't hold at 4000, it will drop further.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 啊?-不是你，是 Sensex 指数
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Huh? - Not you. The Sensex.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这太过分了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is too much.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有机会了，拉凯什
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.12,0:10:41.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's no chance, Rakesh.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}即使今天仍然如此
Dialogue: 2,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even if it holds today...
Dialogue: 3,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再过几天就会跌到3000以下
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in a few days, it'll drop below 3000.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下降的轨迹才刚刚开始，兄弟
Dialogue: 2,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The downward trajectory has only just started, brother.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.32,0:10:54.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wait and watch.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这一次，哈沙德完蛋了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This time, Harshad is finished.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们不应该草率行事，大肆收购
Dialogue: 2,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We shouldn't be hasty and go on a buying spree.
Dialogue: 3,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须像狐狸一样悄悄行动
Dialogue: 2,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to be stealthy, like a fox.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，这次我们很幸运
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look. This time, we were lucky.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们所有的损失都将转化为利润
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.88,0:11:06.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All our losses will get converted into profits.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没错...血赚一笔
Dialogue: 2,0:11:06.96,0:11:09.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}True... Our a***s were on fire!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还好我们只签了一些……
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.00,0:11:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's good we only singed some p*bes.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你控制不了你的舌头，也控制不了你的膀胱
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You have no control over your tongue, nor your bladder.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我只是...-胡说八道！
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- I was just... - What nonsense!
Dialogue: 3,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:16.64,0:11:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们这次勉强活了下来，但这次不能再这样下去了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We scraped through this time but this can't go on.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我觉得..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:23.56,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是退休的好时机
Dialogue: 2,0:11:23.56,0:11:27.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...this is the right time to get out of this casino and retire.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 退休?-你在说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Retire? - What are you saying?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们计划了这一切，只是为了留在市场上
Dialogue: 2,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We planned all this, only to stay in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说要离开市场？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And you're talking of leaving the market?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的不是离开市场
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.84,0:11:37.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm not talking about leaving the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天我决定..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:37.92,0:11:39.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Today, I have decided...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把自己从这些糟心交易中解放出来
Dialogue: 2,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to free myself from this trading mess.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我需要刺激，我可以去拉斯维加斯
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If I need excitement, thrill, I'll go to Vegas.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:48.68,0:11:49.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right?
Dialogue: 3,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从现在开始，只做价值投资
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.16,0:11:54.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}From now on, only value investing.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}价值投资
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Just value investing.
Dialogue: 3,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And...
Dialogue: 3,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会选好的公司，好的股票..
Dialogue: 2,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll pick good companies, good shares...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}投入大量资金，然后等待长远的发展
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...invest big amounts... ...and just wait for long term.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}日复一日的投机交易都是胡说八道
Dialogue: 2,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Day to day trading is nonsense.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}专注于伟大的梦想..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Focus on the big dream...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后赚几百万
Dialogue: 2,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and make millions.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 也许几十亿-也许几万亿
Dialogue: 2,0:12:12.28,0:12:14.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Maybe billions. - Maybe trillions.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 3,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是在市场上交易的最佳时机
Dialogue: 2,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the perfect time to trade in the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔很快就会退出市场
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, Mehta will soon be out of the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sensex 指数将从3000点跌至2500点
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.92,0:12:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sensex will drop from 3000 to 2500.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那之后，利润就来自于购买
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And after that, the profit lies in buying.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看，我不能简单地解释长期的故事
Dialogue: 2,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, I can't explain the story of long-term in short.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在20到25年内，市场将上升到..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In 20 to 25 years, the market will rise to...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}三万五到四万
Dialogue: 2,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...35,000 to 40,000.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它不会从3000变成零
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.72,0:12:41.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not going to go from 3000 to zero.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在是做公牛的时候了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.64,0:12:44.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the time to be a bull.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}熊队的日子一去不复返了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Gone are the days of playing Bears and nibbling peanuts.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 嘿，兄弟...-别跟我说”嘿，兄弟” ，我在讲道理
Dialogue: 2,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hey, Bhai... - Don't "Hey Bhai" me, I'm talking sense.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我的预测是正确的..
Dialogue: 2,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If my prediction is correct...
Dialogue: 3,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁知道呢，我可能会成为下一个大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:12:51.88,0:12:54.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...then who knows, I could be the next Big Bull.
Dialogue: 3,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“现在已经跌破4000了”
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Bhushan] 'We're past 4000 now.'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sensex指数已经触底了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market has sunk so low... ...the Sensex is scraping the floor.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}股票市场变成了杂鱼市场
Dialogue: 2,0:13:13.88,0:13:16.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The share market has turned into a fish market.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在听吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you listening?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直到去年，每个人都在买入
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.56,0:13:21.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Up until last year, everyone was buying.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而现在，突然之间，整个世界都在卖出
Dialogue: 2,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And today, all of a sudden, the whole world is selling.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们的客户都吓呆了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.04,0:13:27.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Our jobbers were petrified.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好像他们要被愤怒的人群殴打似的
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As if they were going to be bashed up by the angry crowd.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 每个人都很害怕-他们当然害怕
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Everyone is scared. -[Ashwin] 'Of course they are scared.'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:33.96,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么不害怕呢
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.96,0:13:34.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Why won't they be scared?'
Dialogue: 3,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场下跌了500多点
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The market has dropped by more than 500 points.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:37.76,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有Polo... Polo一下子从510下降到了300
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.76,0:13:42.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And Polo... Polo has dropped to 510 from 300 in a snap.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 兄弟我们得赶紧想个策略-策略？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.64,0:13:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Brother, we need to think of a strategy soon. - Strategy?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:46.04,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么样的策略？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.04,0:13:46.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What kind of strategy?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们现在只剩下希望了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All we are running on, is hope.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且希望也快用没了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And we're slowly losing that too.
Dialogue: 3,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先想想我们要怎么偿还 NHB 的钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now start thinking how will we repay NHB's money?
Dialogue: 3,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是你第一次看到股市下跌吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Is this the first time you are seeing the market fall?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}(哈沙德)“已经很长时间没有开盘了，很明显会下跌”
Dialogue: 2,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'It has opened after a long time. It's obvious it'll dip.'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拂去一些灰尘，然后再次升起
Dialogue: 2,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It'll lick some dust and rise again.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你忘了吗? 我们是从坠机开始的
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And have you forgotten? We started with a crash.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“有什么新鲜事吗? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:14:09.72,0:14:10.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'What's new about it?'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}最新情况是，哈沙德，这次... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's new, Harshad, is that this time...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们就是坠机的原因
Dialogue: 2,0:14:15.72,0:14:17.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we are the reason for the crash.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那更好，我们是市场之王
Dialogue: 2,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Even better. We're the kings of the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们可以让它下跌，那我们也可以让它再涨上去
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we can cause it to fall, we can make rise it too.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}风向对哈尔沙德有利
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The wind is blowing in Harshad's favour.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它会在我们的命令下改变方向
Dialogue: 2,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it will change its course on our command.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在在这次事故之后，我们要怎么还钱？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:28.36,0:14:31.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And now after this crash, how will we return Pherwani's money?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道这个数目有多大，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You do know how big the amount is, don't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我可以进来吗，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Kashmira] 'May I come in, sir?'
Dialogue: 3,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}卡什米拉，我告诉过你我今天不想被打扰
Dialogue: 2,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Kashmira, I told you I don't want to get disturbed today.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，先生，拉希尔先生在线上
Dialogue: 2,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry, sir. But, Mr. Rahil is on the other line...
Dialogue: 3,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他坚持要和你谈谈
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.96,0:14:45.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and he insists on talking to you.
Dialogue: 3,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 帮我接通-好的先生
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Connect me. - Okay, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好，拉希尔
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hello, Rahil.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你好吗?-我... 我很好
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.12,0:15:03.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- How are you? - I'm... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看到市场的情况了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.76,0:15:06.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Have you seen the condition of the market?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，然后呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:07.28,0:15:08.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. So?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我的意思是... ... 你的人让我投资... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil] 'No, I mean... your men asked me to invest...'
Dialogue: 3,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我把我所有的钱都投进去了，我现在被套牢了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and I did. I invested all I had. I'm deep in it now.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉希尔，股市有时会震荡
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rahil, I call the stock market, shock market sometimes.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它可以造成真正的打击
Dialogue: 2,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It can deal a real blow.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时可以赚钱，有时要遭受损失
Dialogue: 2,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}At times you make a profit, at times you incur a loss.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就是市场，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.04,0:15:23.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's what business means, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你在教我做事？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:23.28,0:15:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're lecturing me about the market?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我对股票市场了解多少？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What do I know about the stock market?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你说，你的人说... ‘投资，投资，投资... ’所以，我照做了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.24,0:15:28.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You said, your men said... 'Invest, invest, invest...' So, I did.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在一切都完了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rahil] 'It's all over now.'
Dialogue: 3,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拉希尔，这是股市不是金库
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Rahil, this is the stock market not a treasure chest...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是把手伸进去，就能抽出一大笔钱来
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that you dip your hand and pull out a fortune, when you like.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你投资的这些钱，是你在市场上赚来的，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.44,0:15:36.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this money that you invested, you earned it in the market, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，市场收回了一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, the market took some of it back.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我没拿你的钱”
Dialogue: 2,0:15:39.24,0:15:40.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Harshad] 'I didn't take your money.'
Dialogue: 3,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白你的意思，但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I... I get your point, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，拉希尔，你是我的朋友... ... 所以我要耐心地解释
Dialogue: 2,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look Rahil, you are a friend... ...so I'm explaining patiently.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有很多客户
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have many clients.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不能向每个人解释，是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I can't explain to each one, can I?
Dialogue: 3,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们改天再聊
Dialogue: 2,0:15:50.40,0:15:52.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll talk peacefully some other time.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}布尚，不要在这里抽烟！
Dialogue: 2,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bhushan, don't smoke here!
Dialogue: 3,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Tyagi ]“那么，今天 Sensex 指数跌了多少? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] 'So, how much did the Sensex fall today?'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 下降了570点-哇
Dialogue: 2,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Fell by 570 points. - [Tyagi] 'Wow.'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}准确地说，是12.77% 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}That's 12.77 per cent to be precise.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在证交所的历史上从来没有..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.88,0:16:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Never before in the history of BSE...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在一天之内下降这么多
Dialogue: 2,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...has it dropped so much in a single day.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ AK ]“投资者的财富蒸发了10% 以上”
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[AK] 'That's more than 10 percent investor wealth wiped out.'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信，他们中的大多数都是哈沙德的投资者
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.88,0:16:26.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And I believe, most of them are Harshad's investors.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯..
Dialogue: 2,0:16:26.44,0:16:27.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Hmm...
Dialogue: 3,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然而，哈尔沙德设法偿还了印度国家银行的贷款
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And yet, Harshad managed to repay SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一共50亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All 500 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我只是想知道是谁资助他的？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I just wonder who funded him?
Dialogue: 3,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管是谁，很快就会暴露
Dialogue: 2,0:16:35.96,0:16:38.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Whoever it was, will be exposed soon.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我相信sensex指数也会在议会上讨论
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I believe the sensex will be discussed in the Parliament too.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你确定?-非常确定
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Are you sure? - Pretty sure.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政客们都在关注这个，AK
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Politicians are on this, AK.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈尔沙德从市场上拿走了太多的钱
Dialogue: 2,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad has taken too much money from the market.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Tyagi ]‘他必须全部归还，今年秋天... ... ’
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.88,0:16:53.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Tyagi] 'And he has to return it all. And due to this fall...'
Dialogue: 3,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他的财产减少了一半
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.60,0:16:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...his holdings have been halved.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:58.96,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是时候结束哈尔沙德 · 梅塔的故事了
Dialogue: 2,0:16:58.96,0:17:02.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's time to put an end to this Harshad Mehta story.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天国会议员们就..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:03.92,0:17:05.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Today the members of the parliament debated...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}’ ... 昨天股票市场的突然崩盘... ’
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...the sudden crash at the stock market yesterday...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... ... 导致了史上最大的 Sensex 指数下跌”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:08.08,0:17:10.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that resulted in the biggest Sensex fall ever.'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在反对派领导人的压力下... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Under pressure from the opposition leaders...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府宣布
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...the government announced...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... RBI 将调查这一事件... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that RBI will probe the event...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天，我们的成员..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.88,0:17:17.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Today, the members of the...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 喂?-哈沙德..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hello? - Harshad...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}仔细听我说
Dialogue: 2,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Listen to me carefully.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的15天结束了
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Your 15 days are over.'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要拿回我的钱
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.72,0:17:32.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need my money back.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}斐尔瓦尼先生，你为什么这么担心？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pherwani ji, why do you worry so much?
Dialogue: 3,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我来考虑这些事
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Worrying is my job.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我欠你钱，你会得到的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I owe you the money and you'll get it.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，你不明白
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.04,0:17:40.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, you are not understanding.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行成立了一个调查委员会..
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.96,0:17:43.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI has formed an enquiry committee...
Dialogue: 3,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}检查你与 SBI 的交易
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.56,0:17:45.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...to inspect your transactions with the SBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你明白这意味着什么吗
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.24,0:17:47.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Do you understand what this means?'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这意味着这些家伙随时可能出现在我家门口
Dialogue: 2,0:17:48.04,0:17:51.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It means that these guys can land up any time at my doorstep.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Pherwani ]“我不想那样”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:52.04,0:17:53.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'And I don't want that.'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要我的账簿干干净净，就这样
Dialogue: 2,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want my books clean, that's it.
Dialogue: 3,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Pherwani ]“要么你筹集资金还钱... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:17:57.04,0:17:58.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Either you organise funds...'
Dialogue: 3,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要么让印度国家银行给 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:17:59.08,0:18:00.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...or ask Grindlays to give BRs.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:18:01.08,0:18:02.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, I've understood the problem.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请相信我
Dialogue: 2,0:18:03.44,0:18:04.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Please trust me.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“市场势必会做出反应”
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'The market was bound to react.'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他承认自己是你文章里的大公牛
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.52,0:18:18.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}His whole confession of him being the Big Bull from your article...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是另一个”哈沙德・梅塔是个骗子”的把戏
Dialogue: 2,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is just another "Harshad Mehta is a liar" trick.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“我告诉你，他已经面临着巨大的损失”
Dialogue: 2,0:18:21.92,0:18:24.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'I'm telling you, he's already looking at huge losses.'
Dialogue: 3,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你认为即使在市场上出现这样的损失..
Dialogue: 2,0:18:24.88,0:18:27.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think even after making such losses in the market...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他会停下来吗? 他不会停下来的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:27.44,0:18:29.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he is going to stop? He's not going to stop.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，你说得对他不会..
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.76,0:18:31.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, you're right. He's not...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}除非你能证明这整个行动都是违法的
Dialogue: 2,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...unless you prove that this entire activity is illegal.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在看起来哈沙德从银行贷了款
Dialogue: 2,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Now, it seems like Harshad took a loan from the bank...
Dialogue: 3,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他把它还回去了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.96,0:18:40.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and he returned it.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}虽然有点晚了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Albeit, a bit late.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们改变问题本身呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What if we change the question itself?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许到那时就很难回答了？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe then it will be difficult to answer?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，如果人们认为这是一笔50亿卢比的贷款，那没关系
Dialogue: 2,0:18:46.52,0:18:50.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, if people think it was a loan of 500 crores, that's okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但回到这个问题上，他是从哪里在这么短的时间内得到50亿卢比的呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But to return that, where did he get 500 crores in such a short time?
Dialogue: 3,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他有足够的资产，他人脉真的很广
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.36,0:18:58.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He has enough assets, holdings. He literally knows everyone.
Dialogue: 3,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ DT ]“我的意思是... ... 半个德里的人都跟着他的调子跳舞”
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.92,0:19:01.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[DT] 'I mean... half of Delhi dances to his tune.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对，没错，所以他肯定给了他们什么好处对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:01.24,0:19:04.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right. Exactly. So, he must've sold something, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他没有官方说法是，高摩资本没有做任何交易
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But he didn't. Officially, Growmore has not done any deals.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“这是50亿卢比的问题”
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.52,0:19:08.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'It's a matter of 500 crores.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}市场上的每个人都会知道这件事
Dialogue: 2,0:19:08.92,0:19:10.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Everybody in the market would get to know about it.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说他去了另一家银行？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:11.60,0:19:13.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you saying, he went to another bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果 SBI 是……
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If SBI was f*...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被他愚弄了
Dialogue: 2,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...fooled by him.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么他一定重复了同样的事情..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then he must have repeated the same thing...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一次又一次地和其他几家银行合作
Dialogue: 2,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...with several other banks again and again.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}B******t.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你能查出他去了哪家银行吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.96,0:19:27.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you think you can find out which banks he has gone to?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白你的意思但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I get your point, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你要银行的名字做什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.60,0:19:31.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...what will you do with just the name of the bank?
Dialogue: 3,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想再刊登一个标题..
Dialogue: 2,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I want to print just one more headline...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一篇可以永远铭刻在人们的脑海里的标题
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that will get imprinted in people's minds forever.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:36.44,0:19:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我需要另一个贝拉里抓住这头大公牛的角
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.44,0:19:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I need another Bellary to grab this Big Bull by his horns.
Dialogue: 3,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，我们正在讨论延长信贷期限的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Mr Mehta, we are talking about an extended line of credit.'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“在目前情况下... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Under the present circumstances...'
Dialogue: 3,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“主席不可能给你这么多钱”
Dialogue: 2,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...it is impossible for Grindlays to give you this kind of money. '
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后另一个选择是印度国家银行
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.44,0:19:59.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then the other option is that Grindlays gives BRs to NHB...
Dialogue: 3,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给NHB付的钱提供 BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...for the money that they have paid.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你这么说真有意思
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.44,0:20:01.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's funny you say that.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们记入所有的 NHB 支票到您的帐户
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We credited all the NHB cheques into your account.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的就是把价值50亿的 BRs 给 NHB
Dialogue: 2,0:20:06.44,0:20:09.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}See, all I am saying is to give BRs worth 500 crores to NHB.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只是需要它来记录
Dialogue: 2,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They just need it for documentation purposes.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这只是一张纸，对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it's just a piece of paper, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这不仅仅是一张纸，不再是了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not just a piece of paper. Not any longer.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们有严格的指示要求停止所有的安全交易
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.00,0:20:19.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have strict instructions to stop all security transactions.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}随时都有可能进行审计
Dialogue: 2,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There could be an audit any day.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这真的这么急吗? 今天是星期天
Dialogue: 2,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And is this really this urgent? It's Sunday.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不想在星期天谈生意
Dialogue: 2,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I don't wanna talk business on a Sunday.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I understand that.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}事实上，我只是来打高尔夫球的
Dialogue: 2,0:20:29.04,0:20:31.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In fact, I just came here to play some golf.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我看见你在这儿，所以想到要讨论一下
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I saw you here, so thought of discussing.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，你为什么不试试呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, why don't you try a shot, Mr. Mehta?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好啊
Dialogue: 2,0:20:39.16,0:20:40.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why not?
Dialogue: 3,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有时候，你必须更加小心谨慎
Dialogue: 2,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sometimes, you have to be more delicate.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看起来你好像不会打高尔夫球
Dialogue: 2,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It looks like you don't know how to play golf.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，我经常打板球
Dialogue: 2,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah, I play cricket a lot.
Dialogue: 3,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想我需要伸展一下我的身体
Dialogue: 2,0:20:58.72,0:21:00.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think I need to stretch my body a little bit.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生，是你的大脑没注意到球
Dialogue: 2,0:21:01.36,0:21:04.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Mehta, your mind missed the shot.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是你的身体
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not your body.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也许，你应该坚持玩你擅长的游戏
Dialogue: 2,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe, you should just stick to the game you are good at.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哈沙德，我们已经从煎锅掉进火里了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:25.16,0:21:28.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Harshad, we've fallen out of the frying pan into the fire.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们没必要再坚持了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We don't need to hold our holdings till they hatch.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我们清理 NHB 的证券
Dialogue: 2,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's clear NHB's settlement.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它不是任何其他私人银行，而是印度储备银行的一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:21:33.72,0:21:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's not any other private bank. It's a part of RBI.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:38.12,0:21:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个行长，他已经对你很生气了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:38.12,0:21:41.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And that governor, he's already pissed at you.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}卖掉所有股份，结束这一切
Dialogue: 2,0:21:42.72,0:21:44.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sell the holdings and end this.
Dialogue: 3,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我听说现在你可以在家里建一个高尔夫球场？
Dialogue: 2,0:21:54.28,0:21:57.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I've heard that these days you can set up a golf green at home?
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你自己去查，我们也可以建一个
Dialogue: 2,0:21:59.44,0:22:00.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You find out. We'll get one too.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果我们必须玩他们的游戏，我们就必须学会它，对不对？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:02.56,0:22:04.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If we have to play their game we'll have to learn it, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他怎么说？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:08.08,0:22:09.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What was that he said?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你必须小心谨慎”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.08,0:22:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"You have to be delicate."
Dialogue: 3,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当你和我在一起的时候，我为什么要害怕？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.60,0:22:29.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why should I be scared when you are with me?
Dialogue: 3,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果遇到暴徒..
Dialogue: 2,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What will I do single-handedly if some goons...
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.76,0:22:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里有所有的名单
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.76,0:22:40.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This has all the names.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我从高摩资本拿到了名单”
Dialogue: 2,0:22:41.36,0:22:42.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I got the list from Growmore.'
Dialogue: 3,0:22:44.64,0:22:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:22:44.64,0:22:45.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thanks.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不用谢，但我的名字不能出现在任何地方
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.92,0:22:48.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, but my name mustn't appear anywhere.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我的工作岌岌可危-我甚至不知道你的名字
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.32,0:22:50.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- My job will be at stake. - I don't even know your name.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:50.76,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我怎么能泄露出去呢? 别担心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.76,0:22:52.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How can I leak it? And don't worry.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.16,0:22:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道怎么保护我的线人，你的名字不会暴露的
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.16,0:22:55.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I know how to protect my sources. Your name won't be revealed.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:55.84,0:22:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧
Dialogue: 2,0:22:55.84,0:22:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay.
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}走吧，叔叔，今晚就到这里吧
Dialogue: 2,0:22:59.88,0:23:02.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Let's go, uncle. That's enough for tonight.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:07.60,0:23:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，哈尔沙德的 SBI 骗局根本算不了什么
Dialogue: 2,0:23:07.60,0:23:10.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, Harshad's SBI scam is nothing.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每家银行在证券方面都有一些不规范之处
Dialogue: 2,0:23:10.96,0:23:14.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Every bank has some irregularities with regard to securities.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 我觉得...-高希..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:15.44,0:23:17.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-[Ghosh] 'I think that...' - Ghosh...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}涉及金额有多大？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}How big is it? Number?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，这些账簿都乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 2,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the books are in a complete mess.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}得到确切的数字需要时间，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:23:21.32,0:23:23.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It'll take time to figure out the exact number, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:24.04,0:23:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你还在等什么? 快点
Dialogue: 2,0:23:24.04,0:23:25.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What are you waiting for? Get on with this.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是所有银行的名单..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This is the list of all the banks...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}过去几天哈沙德一直在和他们打交道
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...with whom Harshad was dealing for the past few days.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.08,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 然后呢?-然后... 然后..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:34.08,0:23:36.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- And? - And... So...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有人能给我们一些线索吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is there anyone, who can give us some leads?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我是说在这些银行工作的人？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:38.44,0:23:41.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, someone who works in any of these banks?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}”我们” ？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:42.16,0:23:43.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Us"?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:43.48,0:23:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你是说能给”你”提供线索的人对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.48,0:23:46.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Oh, you mean, someone who can give "you" a lead, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:47.08,0:23:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}德布，这对我们俩来说都是潜在的共同线索
Dialogue: 2,0:23:47.08,0:23:49.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Debu, this is a potential common lead for both of us.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}之后你可以写一篇详细的，经过深入研究的文章
Dialogue: 2,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can write a detailed, and well-researched article later.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是我需要尽快报道这个故事
Dialogue: 2,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But I need to break this story as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 3,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 但如果你不想帮我...-好吧... 好吧..
Dialogue: 2,0:23:53.04,0:23:54.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- But if you don't wanna help me... - Okay... Okay...
Dialogue: 3,0:23:55.00,0:23:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会找人告诉我们细节，好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:55.00,0:23:58.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll look for someone who can get us the details. Okay?
Dialogue: 3,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:23:59.00,0:24:00.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢你
Dialogue: 2,0:24:04.36,0:24:05.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:03.92,0:25:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我想你们也该走了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:03.92,0:25:05.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I think you gentlemen should also leave now.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:06.84,0:25:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，您也应该休息一下，您的压力太大了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:06.84,0:25:10.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, you should also rest. You are taking a lot of stress.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:10.24,0:25:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然，我做完这个就回家
Dialogue: 2,0:25:10.24,0:25:12.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, of course, I'll just finish this and go home.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要我们收拾桌子吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.28,0:25:15.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Should we clear the table?
Dialogue: 3,0:25:15.52,0:25:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不用了，我自己能行
Dialogue: 2,0:25:15.52,0:25:16.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No. I'll manage.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-去吧-晚安，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Carry on. - Good night, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:21.20,0:25:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很快，就是早安了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:21.20,0:25:22.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Soon, it will be Good Morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:23.76,0:25:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}辛苦了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:23.76,0:25:24.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway, thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:34.24,0:25:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Venkitarajan ]“很抱歉这么早打扰您，先生”
Dialogue: 2,0:25:34.24,0:25:36.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] 'Sorry to disturb you so early in the morning, sir.'
Dialogue: 3,0:25:37.60,0:25:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但我们的估计是正确的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:37.60,0:25:39.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But our estimates were right.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:40.08,0:25:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们团队的初步调查有结果了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.08,0:25:43.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}My team has just come back after the preliminary enquiries and...
Dialogue: 3,0:25:44.84,0:25:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:25:44.84,0:25:45.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是印度最大的金融骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It is India's biggest financial scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:50.60,0:25:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}五百亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:25:50.60,0:25:52.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Five thousand crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:25:55.64,0:25:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:25:55.64,0:25:56.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But...
Dialogue: 3,0:25:57.56,0:25:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生... 我明白，但是..
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.56,0:25:59.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, sir... I do understand, but...
Dialogue: 3,0:26:01.60,0:26:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唯一的解决办法就是公之于众
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.60,0:26:03.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, the only way to handle this is to make it public.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:06.28,0:26:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的... 当然
Dialogue: 2,0:26:06.28,0:26:08.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Y-Yes... of course.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:08.32,0:26:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生我会保密的是的
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.32,0:26:11.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, sir. I will keep it discreet. Yes.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:13.44,0:26:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢你，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:26:13.44,0:26:14.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:31.72,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起... 我睡着了... 你找到人了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:31.72,0:26:34.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry... I slept... Did you find anyone?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:34.28,0:26:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是吗? 你找到人了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:34.28,0:26:35.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes? Did you find anyone?
Dialogue: 3,0:26:35.80,0:26:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给你
Dialogue: 2,0:26:35.80,0:26:36.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Here.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:47.00,0:26:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没有
Dialogue: 2,0:26:47.00,0:26:48.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I didn't.
Dialogue: 3,0:26:49.16,0:26:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但新闻出版社做到了
Dialogue: 2,0:26:49.16,0:26:50.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But News Press did.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:10.60,0:27:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Debashis ]“根据消息来源，骗局的程度... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:10.60,0:27:12.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Debashis] "According to the sources, the extent of the scam..."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:12.80,0:27:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 预计在200亿里亚尔左右”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:12.80,0:27:16.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...is expected to be in the region of Rs. 2000 crores."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:16.48,0:27:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“他们怀疑，剩下的300亿卢比缺口... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:16.48,0:27:19.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"And they suspect that the remaining 3000 crores gap..."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:19.36,0:27:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 可能是由于银行，包括某些证券... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:19.36,0:27:22.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...is probably caused by banks including certain securities..."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:22.52,0:27:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 在他们的报告中，可能没有记录到SGL中”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.52,0:27:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...in their report that may not be part of the SGL records."
Dialogue: 3,0:27:27.00,0:27:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新闻出版社从哪里得到这些细节？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:27.00,0:27:28.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Where is News Press getting these details?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:29.40,0:27:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是... 在过去的十天里我已经和一百个人交谈过了..
Dialogue: 2,0:27:29.40,0:27:31.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean... I've spoken to a hundred people in the last ten days...
Dialogue: 3,0:27:32.20,0:27:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有人透露任何信息
Dialogue: 2,0:27:32.20,0:27:33.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and no one's even uttered a word.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:34.08,0:27:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们可能有一些机密消息来源
Dialogue: 2,0:27:34.08,0:27:36.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They may have some confidential source.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:36.80,0:27:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所有的资料来源都不像你的线人 ，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:27:36.80,0:27:39.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All the sources are not like your 'Karamchand', right?
Dialogue: 3,0:27:41.08,0:27:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:41.08,0:27:41.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:42.44,0:27:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个消息来源于体制内的高层
Dialogue: 2,0:27:42.44,0:27:45.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a major source. Someone in the system, and very senior.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:46.24,0:27:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们钓到了一些大鱼
Dialogue: 2,0:27:46.24,0:27:47.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They've netted some big fish.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:47.28,0:27:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这条大鱼张开了嘴
Dialogue: 2,0:27:47.28,0:27:48.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And this big fish has opened his mouth.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:53.64,0:27:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“先生，我希望你看了新闻”
Dialogue: 2,0:27:53.64,0:27:55.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Ghosh] 'Sir, I hope you read the news.'
Dialogue: 3,0:27:55.76,0:27:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:27:55.76,0:27:56.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:57.20,0:27:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 先生，德里现在很恐慌-早上好
Dialogue: 2,0:27:57.20,0:27:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sir, Delhi is in panic. - Good morning.
Dialogue: 3,0:27:59.88,0:28:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}财政部长办公室一直在不停地打电话
Dialogue: 2,0:27:59.88,0:28:02.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The finance minister's office has been calling incessantly.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:04.04,0:28:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他们有什么要说的?-他们没说什么
Dialogue: 2,0:28:04.04,0:28:06.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What do they have to say? - Sir, nothing much.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们只想和你说话，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:28:06.08,0:28:07.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}They'll only speak with you, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:09.48,0:28:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，我来处理
Dialogue: 2,0:28:09.48,0:28:10.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Alright, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:16.96,0:28:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种情况以前从未发生过，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.96,0:28:18.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This has never happened before, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行行长召开新闻发布会
Dialogue: 2,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, the RBI governor holding a press conference...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:22.96,0:28:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回应报纸上的一篇文章
Dialogue: 2,0:28:22.96,0:28:25.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...in reply to a newspaper article.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:25.80,0:28:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这可能引起更多的猜测和更多的问题
Dialogue: 2,0:28:25.80,0:28:28.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This could give rise to more speculation and more questions.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:29.76,0:28:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是媒体，他们肯定会问问题的
Dialogue: 2,0:28:29.76,0:28:31.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's the Press, they are bound to ask questions.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:33.48,0:28:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}此外，可能还有一些问题... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:33.48,0:28:35.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And moreover, there could be some questions...
Dialogue: 3,0:28:35.84,0:28:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们可能无法回答
Dialogue: 2,0:28:35.84,0:28:38.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...which we might not have answers to.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:38.68,0:28:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不需要回答每一个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:28:38.68,0:28:40.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man1] 'You need not answer every single question.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:41.44,0:28:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你只需要否认这个骗局的规模如此之大”
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.44,0:28:44.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'You just need to deny that the scam is of such proportions.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:45.24,0:28:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}500亿是个震撼人心的数字
Dialogue: 2,0:28:45.24,0:28:48.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'5000 crores is a number that can shake anyone.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:48.96,0:28:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只要向他们解释... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:28:48.96,0:28:50.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Just explain to them...'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:51.12,0:28:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}’ ... 骗局没有这篇文章... ’
Dialogue: 2,0:28:51.12,0:28:52.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that the scam is not as big...'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:52.92,0:28:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所说的那么大
Dialogue: 2,0:28:52.92,0:28:54.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...as this article says.'
Dialogue: 3,0:28:54.48,0:28:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}老实说，先生，我怎么能这么做呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:54.48,0:28:56.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Honestly, sir, how can I do this?
Dialogue: 3,0:28:57.60,0:29:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我凭什么否认事实？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:57.60,0:29:01.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, on what basis do I deny so many facts? Huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:01.56,0:29:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是，我怎么能欺骗公众呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:01.56,0:29:04.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I mean, how can I deny something that is the truth?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:05.04,0:29:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}现在... 现在在我的认知里
Dialogue: 2,0:29:05.04,0:29:07.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Something that is now... now in my knowledge.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:07.56,0:29:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}总督先生，总理将会..
Dialogue: 2,0:29:07.56,0:29:09.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man1] 'Mr. Governor, the Prime Minister will be...'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:09.88,0:29:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 如果这样的消息伤害了我们的经济改革，我们会非常难办”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.88,0:29:12.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...very upset if such news hurts our economic reforms.'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:13.48,0:29:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“请让我们想出一个办法来驳斥这些指控”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:13.48,0:29:16.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Please, let us figure out a way how to refute these allegations.'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:18.08,0:29:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，先生，我明白
Dialogue: 2,0:29:18.08,0:29:19.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yeah... Yes, sir. I understand.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:20.28,0:29:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“梅塔先生的最新情况如何? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.28,0:29:21.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Man1] 'And what's the update on Mr. Mehta?'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:23.00,0:29:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嗯... 是的，调查也在进行中
Dialogue: 2,0:29:23.00,0:29:25.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uhm... Yes. That investigation is on too.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:26.24,0:29:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好，这应该是我们的重点
Dialogue: 2,0:29:26.24,0:29:28.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Good. That should be our focus.'
Dialogue: 3,0:29:30.44,0:29:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好的，先生
Dialogue: 2,0:29:30.44,0:29:31.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Right, sir.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:45.36,0:29:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔先生给你的支票
Dialogue: 2,0:29:45.36,0:29:47.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The cheques that Mr. Mehta gave you...
Dialogue: 3,0:29:48.32,0:29:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 那些...-那些支票已经兑现了
Dialogue: 2,0:29:48.32,0:29:49.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Those... - Those cheques have been cleared.
Dialogue: 3,0:29:52.20,0:29:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，你也把它们从你的账本上清除了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:52.20,0:29:54.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, have you cleared them off your books too?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:54.72,0:29:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么意思？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:54.72,0:29:55.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:56.36,0:29:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也就是说，你没有支票，但你必须登记明细账
Dialogue: 2,0:29:56.36,0:29:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Meaning, you don't have the cheques, but you must have the details?
Dialogue: 3,0:29:59.52,0:30:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[穆克吉]‘给我看看记录’
Dialogue: 2,0:29:59.52,0:30:00.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Mukherjee] 'Show me the records.'
Dialogue: 3,0:30:06.44,0:30:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里
Dialogue: 2,0:30:06.44,0:30:08.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}There's Mr. Mehta.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:11.40,0:30:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听着，他在我们这有个账户，他和我们做生意，他可以..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:11.40,0:30:14.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Look, he has an account with us, he does business with us. He can...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:14.80,0:30:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他想取多少钱都可以
Dialogue: 2,0:30:14.80,0:30:17.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}He can always withdraw as much money as he wants to.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:17.68,0:30:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是你把钱转到他的账户上了，对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:17.68,0:30:20.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But you transfer the money to his account, right?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:21.08,0:30:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以也许你可以给我们看看..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:21.08,0:30:22.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, maybe you would like to show us...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:22.88,0:30:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}转到他的个人账户上吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:22.88,0:30:25.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...the transactions to his personal accounts then?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:25.28,0:30:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，不，我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 2,0:30:25.28,0:30:26.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, no, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:27.24,0:30:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的意思是..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:27.24,0:30:28.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What I mean is that...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:29.12,0:30:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}几天前他做了一笔即期交易
Dialogue: 2,0:30:29.12,0:30:31.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...he had brokered a ready-forward transactions a few days back.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:32.52,0:30:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以钱是打到他账户上的，他肯定用过了
Dialogue: 2,0:30:32.52,0:30:34.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, the money came to his account. He must've used it...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:35.28,0:30:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用于其他目的
Dialogue: 2,0:30:35.28,0:30:36.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...for some other purposes.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:36.08,0:30:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你是和谁做的这个远期交易？
Dialogue: 2,0:30:36.08,0:30:39.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And who did you do this ready-forward transaction with?
Dialogue: 3,0:30:45.04,0:30:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}作为国家中央银行..
Dialogue: 2,0:30:45.04,0:30:46.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}As the central bank of the country...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:47.20,0:30:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们断然否认这个骗局的严重性
Dialogue: 2,0:30:47.20,0:30:51.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we categorically deny that the scam is of such proportions.
Dialogue: 3,0:30:53.72,0:30:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}具体细节到等
Dialogue: 2,0:30:53.72,0:30:55.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The details would only be known...
Dialogue: 3,0:30:56.48,0:31:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}经过 RBI 小组的全面调查
Dialogue: 2,0:30:56.48,0:31:00.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...after a full investigation by the RBI team...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:00.96,0:31:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些银行的证券资产
Dialogue: 2,0:31:00.96,0:31:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...into the security holdings of these banks.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:05.12,0:31:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以在那之前我请求你不要..
Dialogue: 2,0:31:05.12,0:31:07.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, till then, I request you not to...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:07.56,0:31:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}盲目的报道
Dialogue: 2,0:31:07.56,0:31:09.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...blindly speculate, and...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:10.32,0:31:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让有关当局做他们的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:31:10.32,0:31:12.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...let the concerned authorities do their job.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:12.16,0:31:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你是怎么得出结论的
Dialogue: 2,0:31:12.16,0:31:13.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, how did you arrive at the conclusion...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:13.92,0:31:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}骗局没有500亿卢比吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:13.92,0:31:16.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that the scam is not 5,000 crores?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:16.20,0:31:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们知道体制内部出了问题
Dialogue: 2,0:31:16.20,0:31:18.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We know that there's a problem in unit 64.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:18.20,0:31:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你搞定了吗?-还没
Dialogue: 2,0:31:18.20,0:31:19.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Have you sorted it out? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:19.92,0:31:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道债券存在多少问题吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:19.92,0:31:21.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you know how much problem exists in bonds?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:21.80,0:31:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 损失有多大?-我们正在计算
Dialogue: 2,0:31:21.80,0:31:24.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- What is the extent of that loss? - We're calculating that.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:24.80,0:31:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你到底知不知道假BRs
Dialogue: 2,0:31:24.80,0:31:27.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Do you even know the extent of fake BRs...
Dialogue: 3,0:31:27.20,0:31:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 在市场上的流通成都，行长先生？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:27.20,0:31:29.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that are circulating in the market, Mr. Governor?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:29.36,0:31:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“你有没有意识到这样一个事实，假冒的 BRs 已经几乎... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:31:29.36,0:31:32.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Reporter 1] 'Have you been aware of the fact that fake BRs have been almost...'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:32.12,0:31:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ... 成为一个既定的市场惯例?-我们正在进行审计
Dialogue: 2,0:31:32.12,0:31:34.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- ...an established market practice? - We're conducting an audit.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:35.08,0:31:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你知道投资组合资金是怎么回事吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:35.08,0:31:37.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, do you know what was happening with portfolio money?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么公共服务单位会有这么多钱进来？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:37.40,0:31:39.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Why was so much money from PSUs coming in?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:39.68,0:31:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 计算好了吗?-还没有
Dialogue: 2,0:31:39.68,0:31:42.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Have those calculations been made? - Not yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:42.92,0:31:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你凭什么说这个骗局不是500亿？
Dialogue: 2,0:31:42.92,0:31:46.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Then on what basis are you saying that the scam is not 5,000 crores?
Dialogue: 3,0:31:47.92,0:31:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 你为什么不重视这个骗局?-听着这只是个估计
Dialogue: 2,0:31:47.92,0:31:51.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Why are you downplaying the scam? - Look, this is just an estimation.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:52.28,0:31:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Venkitarajan ]“这是我们的理解”
Dialogue: 2,0:31:52.28,0:31:53.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] 'This is our understanding.'
Dialogue: 3,0:31:53.88,0:31:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们是专家，让我们来做我们的工作
Dialogue: 2,0:31:53.88,0:31:56.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are the specialists and we know our job.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:56.48,0:31:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那么，行长先生，你觉得你对此毫无头绪
Dialogue: 2,0:31:56.48,0:31:59.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, Mr. Governor, you are admitting that you have no clue.
Dialogue: 3,0:31:59.48,0:32:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然而，你却坚信这个数字不可能是500亿卢比
Dialogue: 2,0:31:59.48,0:32:02.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yet, you are adamant about the fact that the amount cannot be 5,000 crores.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:07.16,0:32:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们要保护的是谁？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:07.16,0:32:08.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Who are we trying to protect here?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起，记者会结束了，谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sorry, no more questions. Thank you.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生， NHB？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, NHB?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:19.24,0:32:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一方面，我们试图保住颜面
Dialogue: 2,0:32:19.24,0:32:21.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}On the one hand, we are trying to save face to contain the havoc...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:21.64,0:32:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}并且减少这个骗局造成的损失
Dialogue: 2,0:32:21.64,0:32:23.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...that this scam has created.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:24.32,0:32:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}另一方面..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:24.32,0:32:25.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And on the other...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:26.48,0:32:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是印度储备银行的全资子公司
Dialogue: 2,0:32:26.48,0:32:29.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...NHB, which is a wholly-owned subsidiary of the RBI...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:29.72,0:32:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给哈萨德送钱来保护他
Dialogue: 2,0:32:29.72,0:32:32.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...is rolling out cash to Harshad to save his back!
Dialogue: 3,0:32:33.80,0:32:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}梅塔拿整个系统开了个玩笑
Dialogue: 2,0:32:33.80,0:32:35.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mehta has made a joke of this system.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:36.56,0:32:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你认为菲尔瓦尼先生也参与了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:36.56,0:32:38.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, do you think Mr. Pherwani might also be involved?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:39.56,0:32:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我倒愿意相信他与此事无关
Dialogue: 2,0:32:39.56,0:32:42.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well, I'd like to believe he's not involved.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:42.72,0:32:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是像这样的机构..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:42.72,0:32:44.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But when an institution like the...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:45.00,0:32:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... NHB 处理如此大量的交易..
Dialogue: 2,0:32:45.00,0:32:47.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...NHB deals in such high volume transactions...
Dialogue: 3,0:32:47.96,0:32:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他不可能不知情
Dialogue: 2,0:32:47.96,0:32:49.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...can't be without Pherwani's nod.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:49.88,0:32:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先生，你为什么不直接跟他谈谈？
Dialogue: 2,0:32:49.88,0:32:51.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sir, why don't you speak to him directly?
Dialogue: 3,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须找到一个更聪明的方法来处理这个问题
Dialogue: 2,0:32:55.16,0:32:57.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We have to find a smarter way to deal with this.
Dialogue: 3,0:32:57.64,0:32:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[拉吉迪普]“尽管他否认... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:32:57.64,0:32:58.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Rajdeep] "Despite his denial..."
Dialogue: 3,0:32:59.20,0:33:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行行长
Dialogue: 2,0:32:59.20,0:33:01.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...the RBI governor was unable to answer a single question..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:01.64,0:33:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}连记者的一个问题都回答不了
Dialogue: 2,0:33:01.64,0:33:03.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...from the press satisfactorily."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:03.44,0:33:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“这个骗局反映了银行体系的腐败... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:03.44,0:33:05.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"The scam is a reflection of the rot in the banking system..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:05.80,0:33:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 以及印度储备银行监管不力”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:05.80,0:33:07.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...and the inadequate monitoring by the RBI."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:08.16,0:33:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“市场的某些领域对印度储备银行”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:08.16,0:33:10.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"Certain sections of the market are extremely critical..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:10.08,0:33:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}”的徒劳调查极为关键”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:10.08,0:33:12.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...of the ham-handed investigation of the RBI..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:12.56,0:33:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 因为他们相信政府只是想... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:12.56,0:33:14.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...as they believe that the government is simply trying..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:14.48,0:33:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 把事情掩盖起来... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:14.48,0:33:16.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...to sweep the matter under the carpet..."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:16.36,0:33:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}” ... 越来越多的骷髅可能会从壁橱里滚出来”
Dialogue: 2,0:33:16.36,0:33:18.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}"...as more skeletons are likely to tumble out of the closet."
Dialogue: 3,0:33:20.28,0:33:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以，现在我们也把印度央行行长变成了一个恶棍？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:20.28,0:33:22.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So, now we're also turning the RBI governor into a villain?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:23.08,0:33:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果你不想发表这篇文章
Dialogue: 2,0:33:23.08,0:33:25.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}If you don't want to publish this, why don't I give you the transcript...
Dialogue: 3,0:33:25.12,0:33:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我直接把发布会的整个过程全部发表出来？
Dialogue: 2,0:33:25.12,0:33:27.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...of the entire press conference and you can print that?
Dialogue: 3,0:33:29.12,0:33:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不，我更喜欢这个
Dialogue: 2,0:33:29.12,0:33:30.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}No, I like this better.
Dialogue: 3,0:33:30.60,0:33:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 谢谢-继续写完
Dialogue: 2,0:33:30.60,0:33:31.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Thank you. - Finish it.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:12.84,0:34:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这咖啡是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 2,0:34:12.84,0:34:14.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's with this coffee!
Dialogue: 3,0:34:14.64,0:34:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太难喝了
Dialogue: 2,0:34:14.64,0:34:15.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's terrible.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:22.76,0:34:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天，反对派再一次... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:22.76,0:34:24.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'Today, once again, the opposition...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:24.56,0:34:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 在议会中制造噪音... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:24.56,0:34:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...made a noise in the parliament...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:26.52,0:34:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关于价值500亿卢比的违法行为
Dialogue: 2,0:34:26.52,0:34:29.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...about irregularities worth 5000 crores...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:29.96,0:34:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行行长的新闻发布会也受到质疑
Dialogue: 2,0:34:29.96,0:34:32.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'RBI Governor's press conference was also questioned...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:33.00,0:34:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有人要求成立一个联合委员会
Dialogue: 2,0:34:33.00,0:34:35.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...and there were demands For a Joint Parliamentary Committee...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:35.32,0:34:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ ... 对此事进行调查... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:34:35.32,0:34:37.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to carry out investigations in this matter...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:37.92,0:34:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}财政部长向反对派保证... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:37.92,0:34:40.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'The finance minister assured the opposition...'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:40.88,0:34:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府将很快进行公正的法律调查
Dialogue: 2,0:34:40.88,0:34:45.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...that the government will soon conduct an unbiased legal investigation.'
Dialogue: 3,0:34:45.84,0:34:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度时报再一次发挥了作用
Dialogue: 2,0:34:45.84,0:34:47.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once again, TOI is making a difference.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:48.04,0:34:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是每个人都有胆量站起来反对梅塔先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:34:48.04,0:34:50.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not everyone will have had the guts to first go against Mr. Mehta...
Dialogue: 3,0:34:50.64,0:34:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后是印度储备银行行长
Dialogue: 2,0:34:50.64,0:34:51.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and then, the RBI governor.
Dialogue: 3,0:34:55.04,0:34:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-苏切塔!-[鼓掌]
Dialogue: 2,0:34:55.04,0:34:58.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Sucheta! -[applauds]
Dialogue: 3,0:35:03.68,0:35:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}苏切塔，我已经送给你足够多的书了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:03.68,0:35:06.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Sucheta, I've gifted you enough books.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:06.76,0:35:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}下次，我得送你一些酒杯
Dialogue: 2,0:35:06.76,0:35:10.00,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Next time, I will have to gift you some wine glasses.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:10.56,0:35:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那你为什么还不送呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:10.56,0:35:12.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So why haven't you?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:12.24,0:35:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你总是在这里
Dialogue: 2,0:35:12.24,0:35:13.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You're always here.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:14.72,0:35:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}无论如何，德布 · 莫沙伊..
Dialogue: 2,0:35:14.72,0:35:16.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway, Debu Moshai...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:16.96,0:35:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么要喝酒？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:16.96,0:35:18.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...what's the occasion for wine?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:19.24,0:35:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Sucheta ]“这篇文章在议会引起了轩然大波? ”
Dialogue: 2,0:35:19.24,0:35:21.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Sucheta] 'The uproar that the article caused in the parliament?'
Dialogue: 3,0:35:21.88,0:35:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}议会的喧嚣不是什么大事
Dialogue: 2,0:35:21.88,0:35:24.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uproar in the parliament is no big deal.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:24.12,0:35:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 嗯?-总是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:35:24.12,0:35:25.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Hmm? - That always happens.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:25.84,0:35:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 他们是政客-嗯
Dialogue: 2,0:35:25.84,0:35:27.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- They're politicians. - Hmm.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:27.88,0:35:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尖叫是他们工作的一部分
Dialogue: 2,0:35:27.88,0:35:29.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Screaming is part of their job profile.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:29.84,0:35:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们简历上要写分贝值的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:29.84,0:35:32.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Decibel levels are at the top on their CVs...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}证明声音有多大
Dialogue: 2,0:35:33.00,0:35:34.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...confirming how loud they can be...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:34.68,0:35:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不管怎样，先不说这个..
Dialogue: 2,0:35:34.68,0:35:36.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Anyway, leaving that aside...
Dialogue: 3,0:35:36.56,0:35:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们提前庆祝
Dialogue: 2,0:35:36.56,0:35:38.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are celebrating in advance.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:38.44,0:35:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}虽然新闻明天就要发表了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:38.44,0:35:40.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Though the news will be published tomorrow.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:40.40,0:35:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个值得庆祝的消息是什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:35:40.40,0:35:42.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What's this celebration-worthy news?
Dialogue: 3,0:35:43.24,0:35:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}印度储备银行已经成立了一个委员会来调查这个骗局
Dialogue: 2,0:35:43.24,0:35:46.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}RBI has formed a committee to investigate the scam.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:46.56,0:35:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该委员会将由印度储备银行副行长 r. Janakiraman 领导
Dialogue: 2,0:35:46.56,0:35:51.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it will be headed by... RBI deputy governor R. Janakiraman.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:52.32,0:35:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不错嘛！
Dialogue: 2,0:35:52.32,0:35:53.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Not bad!
Dialogue: 3,0:35:53.60,0:35:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以政府终于承认他们有问题了
Dialogue: 2,0:35:53.60,0:35:57.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}So the government is finally acknowledging that they have a problem.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:58.12,0:35:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}正式的
Dialogue: 2,0:35:58.12,0:35:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Officially.
Dialogue: 3,0:35:59.96,0:36:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 不错-等等..
Dialogue: 2,0:35:59.96,0:36:01.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Not bad. - Wait...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:01.36,0:36:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先别喝酒，我还没有告诉你主要的独家新闻呢
Dialogue: 2,0:36:01.36,0:36:04.12,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Don't drink yet. I haven't told you the main exclusive news yet.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:04.24,0:36:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么独家新闻? 听着我是记者..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:04.24,0:36:06.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What exclusive news? Listen, I'm the journalist...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:06.56,0:36:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁应该得到独家新闻
Dialogue: 2,0:36:06.56,0:36:07.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...who's supposed to get exclusive news.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:08.00,0:36:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的，但我也有我的消息来源
Dialogue: 2,0:36:08.00,0:36:09.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes, but I too have my sources.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:09.96,0:36:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也有自己的线人
Dialogue: 2,0:36:09.96,0:36:13.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I too have my own... 'Karamchand'.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:13.40,0:36:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吧，抱歉
Dialogue: 2,0:36:13.40,0:36:14.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Okay, sorry.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:15.28,0:36:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府已经同意将调查移交给 CBI..
Dialogue: 2,0:36:15.28,0:36:18.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The government has agreed to hand over the investigation to the CBI...
Dialogue: 3,0:36:18.84,0:36:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}将由一名高级军官领导
Dialogue: 2,0:36:18.84,0:36:21.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...and it will be headed by a top rank officer.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:21.36,0:36:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI? 他们是认真的？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:21.36,0:36:23.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}CBI? They've gotten serious, huh?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:24.92,0:36:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也是认真的
Dialogue: 2,0:36:24.92,0:36:26.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'm serious too.
Dialogue: 3,0:36:26.96,0:36:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:26.96,0:36:27.72,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Are you?
Dialogue: 3,0:36:28.96,0:36:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关于什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:36:28.96,0:36:29.88,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}What about?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:29.16,0:37:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- 什么事?-Venkitarajan 先生
Dialogue: 2,0:37:29.16,0:37:30.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Yes? - Mr. Venkitarajan.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:31.24,0:37:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼先生
Dialogue: 2,0:37:31.24,0:37:32.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Pherwani, here.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:33.08,0:37:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“我听说... ... ”
Dialogue: 2,0:37:33.08,0:37:34.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'I've heard...'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:34.64,0:37:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你们办公室的几个人在查我们的账目？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:34.64,0:37:37.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...few men from your office are trying to look into our books?
Dialogue: 3,0:37:38.12,0:37:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼先生，那些不是你的账目
Dialogue: 2,0:37:38.12,0:37:40.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Pherwani, those are not your books.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:41.20,0:37:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你好像忘了..
Dialogue: 2,0:37:41.20,0:37:42.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You seem to have forgotten that...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:42.92,0:37:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}“ NHB 是 RBI 的子公司”
Dialogue: 2,0:37:42.92,0:37:44.92,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] '...NHB is a subsidiary of RBI.'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:46.36,0:37:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你不能就这样帮助你的朋友
Dialogue: 2,0:37:46.36,0:37:48.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You can't help your friends just like that.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:48.80,0:37:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Pherwani ]“不... 不是那样的”
Dialogue: 2,0:37:48.80,0:37:50.56,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'No... It was not like that.'
Dialogue: 3,0:37:51.12,0:37:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这只是一个简单的即期交易，仅此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:37:51.12,0:37:53.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was a simple ready-forward deal, that's all.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:54.48,0:37:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}菲尔瓦尼先生
Dialogue: 2,0:37:54.48,0:37:55.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Mr. Pherwani...
Dialogue: 3,0:37:56.40,0:37:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很晚了，我得睡觉了
Dialogue: 2,0:37:56.40,0:37:58.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's late. I need to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 3,0:37:59.28,0:38:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们能晚点再谈这个吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:37:59.28,0:38:00.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Can we talk about this later?
Dialogue: 3,0:38:00.80,0:38:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}呃... Venkitarajan 先生..
Dialogue: 2,0:38:00.80,0:38:03.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Uh... Mr. Venkitarajan...
Dialogue: 3,0:38:05.40,0:38:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有个建议
Dialogue: 2,0:38:05.40,0:38:06.44,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:07.84,0:38:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Pherwani ]‘允许哈尔沙德延期还债... ... ’
Dialogue: 2,0:38:07.84,0:38:09.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Pherwani] 'Allow Harshad to roll over his dues...'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:09.56,0:38:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 再过两个星期
Dialogue: 2,0:38:09.56,0:38:10.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...for another fortnight.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:12.28,0:38:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后你就可以安心睡觉了
Dialogue: 2,0:38:12.28,0:38:13.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then you will sleep in peace.
Dialogue: 3,0:38:50.04,0:38:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[ Venkitarajan ]“达斯先生，我并不是无缘无故地把你叫到这里来”
Dialogue: 2,0:38:50.04,0:38:52.04,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}[Venkitarajan] 'Mr. Das, I haven't called you here without a reason.'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:52.28,0:38:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我有充分的理由... ..
Dialogue: 2,0:38:52.28,0:38:53.64,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'I must be having a very good reason...'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}直接给调查局局长打电话对吗
Dialogue: 2,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.60,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}'...to call the chief of CBI directly, right?'
Dialogue: 3,0:38:56.60,0:38:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们成立的委员会正在调查这个骗局..
Dialogue: 2,0:38:56.60,0:38:59.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}This committee that we're setting up to investigate this scam...
Dialogue: 3,0:38:59.96,0:39:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要一些额外的帮助
Dialogue: 2,0:38:59.96,0:39:01.68,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...we'll need some additional help.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:02.40,0:39:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有太多的人参与其中
Dialogue: 2,0:39:02.40,0:39:04.32,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}You see, there are too many parties involved.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:04.84,0:39:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太多黑幕交易
Dialogue: 2,0:39:04.84,0:39:07.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Too many underhand dealings that are not above board.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:07.44,0:39:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:07.44,0:39:08.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:09.60,0:39:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很多复杂的高级交易
Dialogue: 2,0:39:09.60,0:39:12.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...too many complex, high-level transactions.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:13.24,0:39:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要清理系统
Dialogue: 2,0:39:13.24,0:39:15.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We need to clean the system.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:15.36,0:39:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为此，我们需要确凿的证据
Dialogue: 2,0:39:15.36,0:39:17.28,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And for that, we need hard evidence.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:18.28,0:39:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有证据我们什么也做不了
Dialogue: 2,0:39:18.28,0:39:19.96,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We can't do anything without the evidence.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:20.88,0:39:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们将彻底调查此事
Dialogue: 2,0:39:20.88,0:39:22.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We will investigate it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:23.92,0:39:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但调查局从未处理过..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:23.92,0:39:26.48,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But CBI has never handled...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:27.24,0:39:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}... 这样一个经济案件
Dialogue: 2,0:39:27.24,0:39:28.36,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...such a financial case.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:30.24,0:39:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们需要你的团队不断..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:30.24,0:39:31.76,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We'll need your team to constantly...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:31.84,0:39:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}支持我们，引导我们
Dialogue: 2,0:39:31.84,0:39:35.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...back us up and guide us at every step.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:35.44,0:39:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当然
Dialogue: 2,0:39:35.44,0:39:36.52,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:37.28,0:39:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们与你同在
Dialogue: 2,0:39:37.28,0:39:38.40,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}We are with you.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:39.32,0:39:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们所要求的只是..
Dialogue: 2,0:39:39.32,0:39:41.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All that we ask for is...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:42.28,0:39:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个好警官来处理这个案子
Dialogue: 2,0:39:42.28,0:39:44.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}...a good officer to handle the investigation.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:44.84,0:39:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一个真正的好警官
Dialogue: 2,0:39:44.84,0:39:46.16,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A really good officer.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:46.84,0:39:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我会给你我最好的
Dialogue: 2,0:39:46.84,0:39:48.20,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}I'll give you the best I have.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:49.00,0:39:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}-马达文-马……
Dialogue: 2,0:39:49.00,0:39:50.24,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}- Madhavan. - Ma...
Dialogue: 3,0:39:51.72,0:39:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}博福斯 · 马达文？
Dialogue: 2,0:39:51.72,0:39:52.84,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Bofors Madhavan?
Dialogue: 3,0:39:54.00,0:39:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的
Dialogue: 2,0:39:54.00,0:39:56.08,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Yes. Same officer.
Dialogue: 3,0:39:58.96,0:39:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太棒了
Dialogue: 2,0:39:58.96,0:39:59.80,Default-L2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Well...